      "content": "The shadows in this parlor grow so long, and so heavy... it feels as though the very air is pressing the life from my lungs. He is gone, and with him, the light has vanished from this wretched world. I find myself longing only for the stillness of the grave, to let the darkness finally take me so I might never feel this hollow ache again. Is there truly no solace left for a soul so broken?",
